[ Upstream commit 21f64e72e7073199a6f8d7d8efe52cd814d7d665 ]

Commit 907a076881f1, forgot that we need to clear old values of
XGMAC_VLAN_TAG register when we switch from VLAN perfect matching to
HASH matching.

Fix it.

